         Breadcrumbs   Student Financial Aid and Scholarships    FAQ    Contact Us        UIC Community Notification of COVID – 19 and Financial Aid Office Contact Information  During this time, the Office of Student Financial Aid and Scholarships is CLOSED at our 1800 SSB location.  As such, all on-site and set appointments will be suspended until the end of the semester, if not longer.  Please know that all financial aid counseling staff is working remotely to support all student needs. Your counselor is assigned by college, and their contact information during this time is listed below. The best manner to reach your counselor during this time is via email.  We appreciate all of your patience during this extraordinary time, and intend to provide continued support to all of our students while maintaining continuity in all financial aid process.        Graduate & Professional Programs       College  SFAS Contact  E-mail      Online Programs  Bianca Sanchez   bsanch5@uic.edu     Pharmacy & Graduate/Professional  Cori McManus   corim@uic.edu     Nursing  Thomas Hardaway   tjhard@uic.edu     Dentistry - Class of 2020 & 2023  Thomas Hardaway   tjhard@uic.edu     Dentistry - Class of 2021 & 2022  Bianca Sanchez   bsanch5@uic.edu          Undergraduate Programs       College  SFAS Contact  E-mail      Arch., Design & the Arts  ZaQuela Taylor   ztaylor@uic.edu     Engineering  ZaQuela Taylor   ztaylor@uic.edu     Applied Health Sciences  Cristina Guzman   crguzman@uic.edu     Business Administration  Cristina Guzman   crguzman@uic.edu     Education  Cristina Guzman   crguzman@uic.edu     CUPPA  Leatra Payne   leatrap@uic.edu     Public Health  Leatra Payne   leatrap@uic.edu     LAS (Last Name: A-L)  Leatra Payne   leatrap@uic.edu     LAS (Last Name: M-Z)  Unassigned   money@uic.edu          Locations       University of Illinois at Chicago  For College of Medicine Students      Student Financial Aid & Scholarships, MC 334  UIC College of Medicine (COM)    1200 W. Harrison 